    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The power is managed by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and delivered through a limited-slip differential. This chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates and updated rod bearings to ensure long-term structural and internal integrity. The suspension architecture remains true to the original M-spec geometry, providing the precise turn-in and feedback expected of the marque. While the exterior and cabin show light, honest wear, the drivetrain remains tight with no leaks or timing chain noise, representing a driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
